  <title>Relatives</title>
  <body>
    <p>(82000)</p>
    <p>Relatives (including negated relatives) are encoded in combinations with pronouns and are
      encoded according to agreement in number and gender. Independent relatives are nouns and are
      not encoded here.</p>
